channel.title: Help to show up some non-autoers:)
channel.description: Okay, I am pretty shure I am saying this for everyone: Cheaters always want more people to join there community. I have many friends who play Runescape and I tell them I use Aryan, they have seen it and saw me use it and they think that they make more money playing legit. Well, we are having a contest on who can make more money in a week and they play RS almost 6-8 hrs a day(I know its alot) and I (with Aryan) can only run 1 bot @ a time because my other computer broke and this one has very little ram. If anyone is interested in donating a little (or alot) to my cause, which will show my friends up and cause them to join the Aryan using community and the forums:) Please dont yell at me I am just trying to get more people in the community. Thanks for reading this and please reply on your thoughts, I will not take anything personal. Anyone? Thx again guys.
